{"_path":"/maps/_database/nosql/nosql","_dir":"nosql","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"NoSQL","description":"非关系型数据库技术，包括 Redis 缓存与数据结构","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"主题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"./redis"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Redis"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 内存数据结构存储与缓存技术"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NoSQL（Not Only SQL）数据库提供了一种非关系型的数据存储方式，适用于大规模数据存储、高并发访问和灵活的数据模型场景。与关系型数据库不同，NoSQL 数据库通常不需要固定的表结构，支持水平扩展，并针对特定数据类型（如键值、文档、列族、图）进行了优化。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本 subdomain 主要关注 Redis 这一内存数据结构存储系统，它在缓存、消息队列、实时分析等场景中广泛应用。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"主题","depth":2,"text":"主题"},{"id":"概述","depth":2,"text":"概述"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_database:nosql:nosql.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_database/nosql/nosql.md","_stem":"6.maps/_database/nosql/nosql","_extension":"md"}